    "privacyTitle": "Privacy Policy",
    "privacyIntroTitle": "Introduction",
    "privacyIntroText": "Checkin OK, operated by Radom UG (haftungsbeschränkt), is committed to protecting your privacy. This policy explains how we handle data when you use our service.",
    "privacyDataTitle": "Data We Process",
    "privacyDataText": "We process attendance files (CSV/Excel) containing worker IDs (NISS/BIS/Limosa) that you upload. Files are processed in volatile memory only and never written to disk or stored in any database. All PII is purged immediately after NSSO transmission.",
    "privacyRetentionTitle": "Data Retention",
    "privacyRetentionText": "Zero data retention for PII. We only store aggregate usage statistics (success/fail counts) for billing purposes. No names, NISS, BIS, or Limosa IDs are ever persisted.",
    "privacyCookiesTitle": "Cookies",
    "privacyCookiesText": "We use only technical cookies essential for the functioning of the application (language preference, session). No tracking or analytics cookies are used.",
    "privacyRightsTitle": "Your Rights",
    "privacyRightsText": "Under the GDPR, you have the right to access, rectify, erase, and port your personal data. Since we do not retain any PII, these rights are automatically fulfilled.",
